 Admissions were to start on May 3, however, this was pushed following the government's declaration of a public holiday to mark Eid-ul-Fitr. Education CS George Magoha was in Nyeri to supervise admissions, as he urged school heads not to send students home over lack of fees or uniform.     Parents at St George's Girls Secondary School as Form One admissions begin on May 4, 2022. /BEN KIRUI